<h1>About Us</h1>
<!--<img class="profile" src="images/cat.jpeg" alt="cat profile">-->
<p style="color:black;">
We are a team of students passionate about solving real-world problems using technology. 
This project, an Indoor + Outdoor Campus Navigation System, was built to simplify how people navigate large and complex campus environments.
Our system combines outdoor GPS-based navigation with detailed indoor mapping to provide a seamless experience. 
Users can search for a classroom or location, get routed to the correct building using real-time location, and then continue navigation inside the building to reach the exact room.
We integrated intelligent search using custom matching algorithms, along with map-based visualization powered by modern web technologies. 
The goal was to make navigation faster, smarter, and more accessible for students, visitors, and faculty.
This project reflects our interest in areas like Artificial Intelligence, mapping systems, and user-centric design. 
Moving forward, we aim to enhance it with features like voice search, real-time updates, and mobile app integration.
</p>
